# Phaser standards

Use Phaser 3 scene classes.

Scenes:
- BootScene loads assets and content.
- TitleScene starts the run.
- GameScene owns play flow.
- ResultsScene shows ending summary.

Implementation rules:
- Use Phaser scene lifecycle correctly: preload/create/update.
- Use scene timers for escalation and queue growth.
- Clean up timers and listeners on shutdown.
- Keep button positions fixed during play.
- Prefer simple text and shape UI before decorative art.